{
  "stem": "523.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he couldn't here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I haven't-- we were corresponding with each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've never, I've never seen him anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you have any idea about what might have happened to him?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I came back to Ediniti, I decided I have to go to school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What will happen to me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So even I have no pencil, no paper, no books, I went to register myself to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because I spoke Russian, they put me in grade four.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd-- I'd lost so many years, but because I spoke Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The funny thing, they asked me math.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did I know math?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They ask me how many kilograms there is in a ton.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a thousand kilograms in a ton.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's why they put me-- I went to go in grade five because I spoke Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said, no, you don't know how many kilograms is in a ton.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when I came back to the people who were living, they were laughing at me, said, how come you didn't know that a thousand kilogram is in a ton?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sounds funny, but-- and I started to go to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "How old were you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "12, 12 years old-- it was the year when I came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I went to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have no pencil, no paper, and there weren't any books.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russian children, they had books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were-- the Russian children came with their families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't had any books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, Russian history and Russian geography, it's very difficult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to remember the names, the dates, the places, it goes back maybe 1,000 years ago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the teacher used to dictate notes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
